com.misc.common.moplaf.solver

Interface SolutionProvider

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, IGeneratorTool, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    SolutionReader, SolutionReaderPattern, Solver, SolverCp, SolverLp
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SolutionProviderImpl, SolutionReaderImpl, SolutionReaderPatternImpl, SolverCpImpl, SolverImpl, SolverLpImpl

    public interface SolutionProvider
extends IGeneratorTool
    A representation of the model object 'Solution Provider'. A SolutionProvider is capable of providing a solution for a given linear formulation (a Generator). Solution is provided as a collection of SolutionLpVars (resp. SolutionLpCons), giving properties of the solution for a particular variable GeneratorLpVar (resp. a particular constraint GeneratorLpCons)

    The following features are supported:

    • Solution
    • Current Solution Nr
    • Code
    See Also:
    SolverPackage.getSolutionProvider()
